This paper deals with data management and interoperability between different database systems, which falls under the category of database systems (cs.DB). Additionally, the paper discusses semantic preservation and information preservation, which are topics related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves querying and searching graph-like data, which is a topic in information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper discusses the development of methods for interoperability, which is a topic in software engineering (cs.SE).
